<SYNC Start=1356288><P Class=ENCC>
No.
<SYNC Start=1357346><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1357522><P Class=ENCC>
-Has the pain been getting worse?<br>-No.
<SYNC Start=1359854><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1360292><P Class=ENCC>
Do you sleep with women<br>and never call them again?
