<SYNC Start=1387016><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1387185><P Class=ENCC>
that's four, one higher than<br>the number of centimeters I'm dilated..
<SYNC Start=1390882><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1391056><P Class=ENCC>
have come and gone with their babies.<br>I'm next. It's my turn. It's only fair.
