<SYNC Start=2105399><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2105603><P Class=ENCC>
-I'm sorry, I can't! I can't!<br>-Yes, you can. I know you can do this.
<SYNC Start=2110131><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
