Oh, God.
<SYNC Start=2336694><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2336901><P Class=ENCC>
-What's the matter now?<br>-I was reliving it.
<SYNC Start=2341463><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2342440><P Class=ENCC>
Do you know what you're gonna<br>call her yet?
<SYNC Start=2345466><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
