<SYNC Start=2354614><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2354819><P Class=ENCC>
And you know what? I love them both.<br>So just pick one, and that'll be it.
<SYNC Start=2360758><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2360925><P Class=ENCC>
Wow, okay. Everyone..
