-And if it's a girl?<br>-I don't wanna say.
<SYNC Start=2435429><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2435633><P Class=ENCC>
Oh, stop. Tell us.<br>We're not gonna want it.
<SYNC Start=2439694><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2439870><P Class=ENCC>
Okay. It's Emma.
