<SYNC Start=2442573><P Class=ENCC>
Emma.
<SYNC Start=2445599><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2449447><P Class=ENCC>
See, I don't want it.
<SYNC Start=2452416><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2452583><P Class=ENCC>
