<SYNC Start=2508632><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2523521><P Class=ENCC>
-That was amazing.<br>-I know.
<SYNC Start=2526456><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2528359><P Class=ENCC>
Hey, do you realize that we may have<br>just changed our lives forever?
<SYNC Start=2534320><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
