<SYNC Start=2548946><P Class=ENCC>
I love you so much.
<SYNC Start=2550379><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2550548><P Class=ENCC>
-Oh, yeah?<br>-Yeah.
<SYNC Start=2552846><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2557087><P Class=ENCC>
You wanna do it again?
<SYNC Start=2558645><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
