<SYNC Start=2560050><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2563494><P Class=ENCC>
Probably.
<SYNC Start=2565291><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2570534><P Class=ENCC>
Aaron Lipman-Guralnick would like<br>to say hello to his future bride.
<SYNC Start=2576404><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2584915><P Class=ENCC>
Wow, he kind of takes your breath away,<br>doesn't he?
<SYNC Start=2588373><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2588552><P Class=ENCC>
He's a keeper.
<SYNC Start=2591316><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2592723><P Class=ENCC>
