<SYNC Start=2595317><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2595492><P Class=ENCC>
Don't you worry. By the time<br>you're old enough to date him..
<SYNC Start=2598359><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2598529><P Class=ENCC>
he's gonna have a different nose.
<SYNC Start=2600622><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2601832><P Class=ENCC>
-How you feeling?<br>-Oh, I'm fine.
<SYNC Start=2606360><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2607171><P Class=ENCC>
I really admire what you're doing.<br>Just raising her all alone.
<SYNC Start=2613167><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2613344><P Class=ENCC>
