<SYNC Start=2621641><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2622419><P Class=ENCC>
Well, then he gets a divorce.<br>It's Ross.
<SYNC Start=2626116><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2628525><P Class=ENCC>
I'm telling you, Rachel, listen to Janice.
<SYNC Start=2631221><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2631395><P Class=ENCC>
They all say they're gonna be there,<br>until they start their real family.
<SYNC Start=2637561><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2638369><P Class=ENCC>
-That's never gonna happen with Ross.<br>-That's what I thought.
<SYNC Start=2643204><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2643374><P Class=ENCC>
I'm lucky if my kid gets to spend<br>a weekend with her father..
<SYNC Start=2646605><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2646777><P Class=ENCC>
and little Miss New Boobs.
