Really?
<SYNC Start=2652143><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2652583><P Class=ENCC>
I hate to be the one to say it..
<SYNC Start=2654915><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2655085><P Class=ENCC>
but, honey, you two are on your own.
<SYNC Start=2660148><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2661225><P Class=ENCC>
Well, that's.. You know, that's..
<SYNC Start=2664194><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2664361><P Class=ENCC>
We've been alone for the last<br>20 minutes and we're doing okay.
<SYNC Start=2668661><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2669800><P Class=ENCC>
Maybe we won't be alone.
<SYNC Start=2671563><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2671735><P Class=ENCC>
Because lately things have been<br>happening between me and Ross.
<SYNC Start=2676695><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2676874><P Class=ENCC>
And right before I went into labor,<br>we had this kiss. You know?
<SYNC Start=2681607><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2681779><P Class=ENCC>
So it might be the beginning<br>of something.
