<SYNC Start=2755548><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2755719><P Class=ENCC>
I was talking to this nurse.<br>Completely forgot.
<SYNC Start=2759815><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2761325><P Class=ENCC>
And so it begins.
<SYNC Start=2764419><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
