She in there?
<SYNC Start=2772162><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2772503><P Class=ENCC>
Yeah. She's putting her down now.<br>That's her.
<SYNC Start=2775836><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2776006><P Class=ENCC>
Isn't it amazing how<br>every baby is beautiful?
<SYNC Start=2779567><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2780010><P Class=ENCC>
Except that one.
<SYNC Start=2781773><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2783514><P Class=ENCC>
